----------------------------------------------------------------------
KrutiDev 010 legacy-font -> Unicode mapping data (SIL wsresources)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The Kruti Dev 010 byte->Unicode transducer in `legacy_krutidev010.go`
(the byte-class definitions and the Pass 0-6 mapping/reorder rules) is a
pure-Go port of the TECkit mapping `KrutiDev010.map` distributed by SIL
International in the silnrsi/wsresources repository. Only the character-
equivalence DATA (byte codes, Unicode code points, and the documented
reorder passes) is ported; no TECkit source code or runtime is included,
and ZERO_WIDTH_JOINER/NON_JOINER are intentionally omitted for searchable
text. The font binaries themselves are NOT included or required.

  Source:  https://github.com/silnrsi/wsresources
  File:    scripts/Deva/legacy/kruti-dev-010/mappings/KrutiDev010.map

